{"surahDetails":{"id":107,"arabicName":"الماعون","banglaName":"সাহায্য সহায়তা","englishName":"Almsgiving","enTranslatedName":"Al-Ma'un","arLocation":"مكية","enLocation":"meccan","totalWords":25,"totalLetters":112,"audio":"http://download.quranicaudio.com/quran/ahmed_ibn_3ali_al-3ajamy/107.mp3","totalAyah":7},"surah":{"id":107,"verses":[{"id":1,"arabic_text":"أَرَءَيۡتَ ٱلَّذِي يُكَذِّبُ بِٱلدِّينِ","bangl_text":"আপনি কি দেখেছেন তাকে, যে বিচারদিবসকে মিথ্যা বলে","english_text":"Have you seen the one who denies the Recompense","page":602,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://everyayah.com/data/ahmed_ibn_ali_al_ajamy_128kbps/107001.mp3"},{"id":2,"arabic_text":"فَذَٰلِكَ ٱلَّذِي يَدُعُّ ٱلۡيَتِيمَ","bangl_text":"সে সেই ব্যক্তি, যে এতীমকে গলা ধাক্কা দেয়","english_text":"For that is the one who drives away the orphan","page":602,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://everyayah.com/data/ahmed_ibn_ali_al_ajamy_128kbps/107002.mp3"},{"id":3,"arabic_text":"وَلَا يَحُضُّ عَلَىٰ طَعَامِ ٱلۡمِسۡكِينِ","bangl_text":"এবং মিসকীনকে অন্ন দিতে উৎসাহিত করে না।","english_text":"And does not encourage the feeding of the poor","page":602,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://everyayah.com/data/ahmed_ibn_ali_al_ajamy_128kbps/107003.mp3"},{"id":4,"arabic_text":"فَوَيۡلٞ لِّلۡمُصَلِّينَ","bangl_text":"অতএব দুর্ভোগ সেসব নামাযীর","english_text":"So woe to those who pray","page":602,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://everyayah.com/data/ahmed_ibn_ali_al_ajamy_128kbps/107004.mp3"},{"id":5,"arabic_text":"ٱلَّذِينَ هُمۡ عَن صَلَاتِهِمۡ سَاهُونَ","bangl_text":"যারা তাদের নামায সম্বন্ধে বে-খবর","english_text":"[But] who are heedless of their prayer","page":602,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://everyayah.com/data/ahmed_ibn_ali_al_ajamy_128kbps/107005.mp3"},{"id":6,"arabic_text":"ٱلَّذِينَ هُمۡ يُرَآءُونَ","bangl_text":"যারা তা লোক-দেখানোর জন্য করে","english_text":"Those who make show [of their deeds]","page":602,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://everyayah.com/data/ahmed_ibn_ali_al_ajamy_128kbps/107006.mp3"},{"id":7,"arabic_text":"وَيَمۡنَعُونَ ٱلۡمَاعُونَ","bangl_text":"এবং নিত্য ব্যবহার্য্য বস্তু অন্যকে দেয় না।","english_text":"And withhold [simple] assistance","page":602,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://everyayah.com/data/ahmed_ibn_ali_al_ajamy_128kbps/107007.mp3"}]}}